r graduating from high school, you should focus on IT! You are our top candidate if you are enthusiastic about IT and technology, outgoing and can express - vocally and in writing - yourself in German as well. As a real team player you also convince with your open and friendly manner? We look forward to hearing from you! Your training with us will give you the best opportunities right from the start. From the beginning, we will provide you with qualified trainers who I will intensively prepare for your tasks. You earn good money: We guarantee above-average trainee remuneration plus many other extras. We offer you challenging and interesting tasks with significant levels of responsibility in a truly international work environment. At HELM we combine the sustainable thinking of a family-owned business with an entrepreneurial mentality that encourages quick decision making and freedom to operate in your business area. Interested? Then please apply with all necessary documents via our application portal. If you have questions, feel free to contact the contact person for this position. What we offer At HELM, we are proud of our history and our international economic success. We know how important a healthy working atmosphere and satisfied employees are for this success. We offer among other things: Professional trainings and language courses Company kindergarten for children between 3 and 7 years of age 30 days of holiday 5 holiday apartments Company pension scheme - increased allowance for direct insurance offered by the Company and/or pension fund Advance towards season ticket for public transport HELM's company restaurant Jetzt bewerben Deutschland United StatesCanada ArgentinaAustraliaBelgiÃ«BrasilDeutschlandEspaÃ±aFranceIndiaIrelandItaliaMÃ©xicoNederlandÃsterreichPortugalSchweizSouth AfricaSverigeUnited KingdomÐ Ð¾ÑÑÐ¸Ñíêµ­ä¸­å½æ¥æ¬ Â© 2020 SH Inc. | Datenschutz | NutzungsbedingungenÂ |Â Datenschutzzentrum | Impressum"
